  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780430/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1674053969\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780430/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1674053969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780430/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1674053969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780430/extras/c70a00904b96cff91d4346d699c47548.avif?t=1674053969\" width=616 height=80 /></span><br><i>In this narrative-driven platformer game, you play as child that runs away to fight the monster she thought was causing trouble in her family. What she found was not what she was expecting.  Fight your way out and find the truth about this mysterious place, told through original hand-drawn cutscenes, completely without text.\" </i><br><br><strong>Using a sword and shield based combat, you have to fight different types of enemies and mechanics through the levels and reach your goal: Find and face the monster to save your family.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780430/extras/50196d52573e24467d9f063226dd4e0a.avif?t=1674053969\" width=616 height=80 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Stylized</strong> pixel-art and hand-drawn cutscenes;<br></li><li><strong>Hand-crafted levels</strong> with increasing complexity;<br></li><li><strong>Tight controls</strong> - optmized controls for gamepads and keyboards;<br></li><li><strong>Original</strong> Soundtrack;</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780430/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1674053969\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780430/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1674053969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780430/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1674053969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780430/extras/c70a00904b96cff91d4346d699c47548.avif?t=1674053969\" width=616 height=80 /></span><br><i>In this narrative-driven platformer game, you play as child that runs away to fight the monster she thought was causing trouble in her family. What she found was not what she was expecting.  Fight your way out and find the truth about this mysterious place, told through original hand-drawn cutscenes, completely without text.\" </i><br><br><strong>Using a sword and shield based combat, you have to fight different types of enemies and mechanics through the levels and reach your goal: Find and face the monster to save your family.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780430/extras/50196d52573e24467d9f063226dd4e0a.avif?t=1674053969\" width=616 height=80 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Stylized</strong> pixel-art and hand-drawn cutscenes;<br></li><li><strong>Hand-crafted levels</strong> with increasing complexity;<br></li><li><strong>Tight controls</strong> - optmized controls for gamepads and keyboards;<br></li><li><strong>Original</strong> Soundtrack;</li></ul>",
